</span><span class="x1lliihq">Pensar en el origen
</span><span class="x1lliihq">No poner nombres ni límites
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Ser un ser razonable no animal
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Pensar antes de hablar
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Buscar el detonante para la reacción
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Meterse la lengua en el culo
</span><span class="x1lliihq">No responsabilizar a un ente
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Responsabilizarse de los actos
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Madurar
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Comparar actitudes con diferentes personas
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Escuchar a los demás pero de verdad
</span><span class="x1lliihq">No lo sabes todo
</span><span class="">Replantearte lo que te haga mal a ti o a otra persona</span></span><span class=""><span class="x3nfvp2 xxymvpz xlshs6z xqtp20y xexx8yu x1uc92m x18d9i69 x181vq82 x12lo8hy x152skdk" aria-hidden="true"><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xn6xy2s"></span><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s">0:22</span></span></span></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1n327nk x18mqm2i xhsvlbd x14z9mp xz62fqu x1wbi8v6"><div class="x1bvqhpb xx3o462 xuxw1ft x78zum5 x6s0dn4 x12lo8hy x152skdk" data-testid="msg-meta"><span class="x1rg5ohu x16dsc37" dir="auto"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px;">0:22</span></span><div class="xhslqc4 x1rg5ohu x7phf20"><span aria-hidden="false" aria-label=" Leído " class="x1rv0e52"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="" fill="currentColor"><title>wds-ic-read</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M14.73 6.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15l.01.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41L7.6 18.01a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05c-.26 0-.52-.11-.71-.3l-4.03-4.09a.99.99 0 0 1 0-1.41.99.99 0 0 1 1.41 0l3.25 3.29 7.99-9.86Zm5.71.12a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15h-.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41l-8.41 10.45a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05a1 1 0 0 1-.71-.3l-1.36-1.26a.55.55 0 0 1-.02-.81l.56-.68c.21-.2.53-.21.75-.03l.71.58 7.71-9.58Z"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></div><span class=""></span><div class="x10l6tqk xyc4j8s xceh6e4"></div></div></div><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 x78zum5 xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xeuugli x2lwn1j x13a6bvl x1q0g3np x6s0dn4 xken49m xexx8yu x18d9i69 x135b78x x11lfxj5 x10l6tqk xwa60dl xfvs6mw xho9bl7"><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 xeuugli x2lwn1j xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xexx8yu x1im30kd x18d9i69 x1djpfga xcxita6"><div></div></div></div></div><div class="x78zum5 xbfrwjf x8k05lb xeq5yr9 x1n2onr6 x1f889gz xpvyfi4" data-testid="addon-bubble-container"></div></div></div></div></div></div></di